        <location filename="../gui/optionsdialog.ui" line="1564"/>
        <source>Blacklist filtered file names from being downloaded from torrent(s).
Files matching any of the filters in this list will have their priority automatically set to &quot;Do not download&quot;.

Use newlines to separate multiple entries. Can use wildcards as outlined below.
*: matches zero or more of any characters.
?: matches any single character.
[...]: sets of characters can be represented in square brackets.

Examples
*.exe: filter '.exe' file extension.
readme.txt: filter exact file name.
?.txt: filter 'a.txt', 'b.txt' but not 'aa.txt'.
readme[0-9].txt: filter &apos;readme1.txt&apos;, &apos;readme2.txt&apos; but not &apos;readme10.txt&apos;.</source>
        <translation>Dodajte na crnu listu filtrirana imena datoteka kako bi se sprečilo preuzimanje sa torrenta.
Datoteke koje odgovaraju bilo kom od filtera na ovoj listi će automatski imati prioritet podešen na „Ne preuzimaj“.

Koristite znakove za novi red da biste odvojili više unosa. Možete koristiti džokere kao što je navedeno u nastavku.
*: podudara se sa nulom ili više bilo kojih znakova.
?: podudara se sa bilo kojim pojedinačnim znakom.
[...]: skupovi znakova mogu biti predstavljeni u uglastim zagradama.

Primeri
*.exe: filtrira ekstenziju datoteke &apos;.exe&apos;.
readme.txt: filtrira tačno ime datoteke.
?.txt: filtrira &apos;a.txt&apos;, &apos;b.txt&apos; ali ne &apos;aa.txt&apos;.
readme[0-9].txt: filtrira &apos;readme1.txt&apos;, &apos;readme2.txt&apos; ali ne &apos;readme10.txt&apos;.</translation>
    </message>
